Package: sqldk
Version: 0.1
Date: 2024-05-25
Title: Manipulate R Data Frames using duckdb SQL
Author: G. Grothendieck <ggrothendieck@gmail.com>
Maintainer: G. Grothendieck <ggrothendieck@gmail.com>
Description: Process one or more SQL statements with duckdb against data frames
  in workspace. Similar in purpose to sqldf package but with duckdb database.
